{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Kg 18:12","book":"2Ki","chapter":18,"verse":12,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" the prophets."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Kg 17:13","book":"2Ki","chapter":17,"verse":13},{"label":"2Kg 18:12","book":"2Ki","chapter":18,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Dan:9:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"All Israel has broken your law and turned away, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 1:3–4","book":"Isa","chapter":1,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 8:5–10","book":"Jer","chapter":8,"verse":5,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" refusing to obey you. The promised curse "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit The curse and the oath"},{"kind":"text","text":" written in the law of Moses, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 28:15","book":"Deu","chapter":28,"verse":15,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 29:16–30:20","book":"Deu","chapter":29,"verse":16,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 2:22","book":"Luk","chapter":2,"verse":22,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" the servant of God, has been poured out on us because we have sinned against him. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 1:3–4","book":"Isa","chapter":1,"verse":3},{"label":"Jr 8:5–10","book":"Jer","chapter":8,"verse":5},{"label":"Dt 28:15","book":"Deu","chapter":28,"verse":15},{"label":"Dt 29:16–30:20","book":"Deu","chapter":29,"verse":16},{"label":"Lk 2:22","book":"Luk","chapter":2,"verse":22}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit The curse and the oath"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Dan:9:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He has carried out his words "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 44:26","book":"Isa","chapter":44,"verse":26,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 44:2–6","book":"Jer","chapter":44,"verse":2,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lm 2:17","book":"Lam","chapter":2,"verse":17,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Zch 1:6","book":"Zec","chapter":1,"verse":6,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" that he spoke against us and against our rulers "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Lit against rulers who ruled us"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 12:17","book":"Job","chapter":12,"verse":17,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 82:2–7","book":"Psa","chapter":82,"verse":2,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 148:11","book":"Psa","chapter":148,"verse":11,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" by bringing on us a disaster that is so great that nothing like what has been done to Jerusalem has ever been done "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lm 1:12","book":"Lam","chapter":1,"verse":12,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lm 2:13","book":"Lam","chapter":2,"verse":13,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 5:9","book":"Ezk","chapter":5,"verse":9,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"text","text":" under all of heaven. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 44:26","book":"Isa","chapter":44,"verse":26},{"label":"Jr 44:2–6","book":"Jer","chapter":44,"verse":2},{"label":"Lm 2:17","book":"Lam","chapter":2,"verse":17},{"label":"Zch 1:6","book":"Zec","chapter":1,"verse":6},{"label":"Jb 12:17","book":"Job","chapter":12,"verse":17},{"label":"Ps 82:2–7","book":"Psa","chapter":82,"verse":2},{"label":"Ps 148:11","book":"Psa","chapter":148,"verse":11},{"label":"Lm 1:12","book":"Lam","chapter":1,"verse":12},{"label":"Lm 2:13","book":"Lam","chapter":2,"verse":13},{"label":"Ezk 5:9","book":"Ezk","chapter":5,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Lit against rulers who ruled us"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Dan:9:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Just as it is written in the law of Moses, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 26:14","book":"Lev","chapter":26,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 28:15","book":"Deu","chapter":28,"verse":15,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dn 9:11","book":"Dan","chapter":9,"verse":11,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" all this disaster has come on us, yet we have not sought the favor of "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 36:13","book":"Job","chapter":36,"verse":13,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 9:13","book":"Isa","chapter":9,"verse":13,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 2:30","book":"Jer","chapter":2,"verse":30,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 5:3","book":"Jer","chapter":5,"verse":3,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mal 1:9","book":"Mal","chapter":1,"verse":9,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"text","text":" the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" our God by turning from our iniquities and paying attention to your truth. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 31:18","book":"Jer","chapter":31,"verse":18,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lv 26:14","book":"Lev","chapter":26,"verse":14},{"label":"Dt 28:15","book":"Deu","chapter":28,"verse":15},{"label":"Dn 9:11","book":"Dan","chapter":9,"verse":11},{"label":"Jb 36:13","book":"Job","chapter":36,"verse":13},{"label":"Is 9:13","book":"Isa","chapter":9,"verse":13},{"label":"Jr 2:30","book":"Jer","chapter":2,"verse":30},{"label":"Jr 5:3","book":"Jer","chapter":5,"verse":3},{"label":"Mal 1:9","book":"Mal","chapter":1,"verse":9},{"label":"Jr 31:18","book":"Jer","chapter":31,"verse":18}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Dan:9:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" kept the disaster in mind and brought it on us, for the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" our God is righteous in all he has done. But we have not obeyed him."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Dan:9:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Now, Lord our God —who brought your people out of the land of Egypt with a strong hand "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 5:15","book":"Deu","chapter":5,"verse":15,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and made your name renowned "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Neh 9:10","book":"Neh","chapter":9,"verse":10,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 32:20","book":"Jer","chapter":32,"verse":20,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" as it is this day —we have sinned, we have acted wickedly. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 5:15","book":"Deu","chapter":5,"verse":15},{"label":"Neh 9:10","book":"Neh","chapter":9,"verse":10},{"label":"Jr 32:20","book":"Jer","chapter":32,"verse":20}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Dan:9:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Lord, in keeping with all your righteous acts, may your anger and wrath "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 32:31–32","book":"Jer","chapter":32,"verse":31,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" turn away from your city Jerusalem, your holy mountain; "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 87:1–3","book":"Psa","chapter":87,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dn 9:20","book":"Dan","chapter":9,"verse":20,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jl 3:17","book":"Jol","chapter":3,"verse":17,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Zch 8:3","book":"Zec","chapter":8,"verse":3,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" for because of our sins and the iniquities of our ancestors, Jerusalem and your people have become an object of ridicule to all those around us."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 32:31–32","book":"Jer","chapter":32,"verse":31},{"label":"Ps 87:1–3","book":"Psa","chapter":87,"verse":1},{"label":"Dn 9:20","book":"Dan","chapter":9,"verse":20},{"label":"Jl 3:17","book":"Jol","chapter":3,"verse":17},{"label":"Zch 8:3","book":"Zec","chapter":8,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Dan:9:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Therefore, our God, hear the prayer and the petitions of your servant. Make your face shine "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 6:25","book":"Num","chapter":6,"verse":25,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 31:17","book":"Psa","chapter":31,"verse":17,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 67:2","book":"Psa","chapter":67,"verse":2,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" on your desolate sanctuary "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lm 5:18","book":"Lam","chapter":5,"verse":18,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" for the Lord’s sake. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Nm 6:25","book":"Num","chapter":6,"verse":25},{"label":"Ps 31:17","book":"Psa","chapter":31,"verse":17},{"label":"Ps 67:2","book":"Psa","chapter":67,"verse":2},{"label":"Lm 5:18","book":"Lam","chapter":5,"verse":18}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Dan:9:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Listen closely, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit Stretch out your ear"},{"kind":"text","text":" my God, and hear. Open your eyes and see our desolations and the city that bears your name. For we are not presenting our petitions before you based on our righteous acts, but based on your abundant compassion. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit Stretch out your ear"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Dan:9:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Lord, hear! Lord, forgive! Lord, listen and act! My God, for your own sake, do not delay, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 44:23","book":"Psa","chapter":44,"verse":23,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 74:10–11","book":"Psa","chapter":74,"verse":10,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" because your city and your people bear your name."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 44:23","book":"Psa","chapter":44,"verse":23},{"label":"Ps 74:10–11","book":"Psa","chapter":74,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Dan:9:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"While I was speaking, praying, confessing my sin and the sin of my people Israel, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 145:18","book":"Psa","chapter":145,"verse":18,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 58:9","book":"Isa","chapter":58,"verse":9,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dn 9:3","book":"Dan","chapter":9,"verse":3,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dn 10:12","book":"Dan","chapter":10,"verse":12,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" and presenting my petition before the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" my God concerning the holy mountain of my God — "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 145:18","book":"Psa","chapter":145,"verse":18},{"label":"Is 58:9","book":"Isa","chapter":58,"verse":9},{"label":"Dn 9:3","book":"Dan","chapter":9,"verse":3},{"label":"Dn 10:12","book":"Dan","chapter":10,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Dan:9:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"while I was praying, Gabriel, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dn 8:16","book":"Dan","chapter":8,"verse":16,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 1:19","book":"Luk","chapter":1,"verse":19,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 1:26","book":"Luk","chapter":1,"verse":26,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" the man I had seen in the first vision, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dn 8:1","book":"Dan","chapter":8,"verse":1,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dn 8:15","book":"Dan","chapter":8,"verse":15,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" reached me in my extreme weariness, about the time of the evening offering. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 29:39","book":"Exo","chapter":29,"verse":39,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Kg 18:36","book":"1Ki","chapter":18,"verse":36,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezr 9:4","book":"Ezr","chapter":9,"verse":4,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dn 8:16","book":"Dan","chapter":8,"verse":16},{"label":"Lk 1:19","book":"Luk","chapter":1,"verse":19},{"label":"Lk 1:26","book":"Luk","chapter":1,"verse":26},{"label":"Dn 8:1","book":"Dan","chapter":8,"verse":1},{"label":"Dn 8:15","book":"Dan","chapter":8,"verse":15},{"label":"Ex 29:39","book":"Exo","chapter":29,"verse":39},{"label":"1Kg 18:36","book":"1Ki","chapter":18,"verse":36},{"label":"Ezr 9:4","book":"Ezr","chapter":9,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Dan:9:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He gave me this explanation: “Daniel, I’ve come now to give you understanding. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dn 8:16","book":"Dan","chapter":8,"verse":16,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dn 10:21","book":"Dan","chapter":10,"verse":21,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Zch 1:9","book":"Zec","chapter":1,"verse":9,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dn 8:16","book":"Dan","chapter":8,"verse":16},{"label":"Dn 10:21","book":"Dan","chapter":10,"verse":21},{"label":"Zch 1:9","book":"Zec","chapter":1,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Dan:9:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"At the beginning of your petitions an answer went out, and I have come to give it, for you are treasured by God. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"by God added for clarity"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dn 10:11","book":"Dan","chapter":10,"verse":11,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dn 10:19","book":"Dan","chapter":10,"verse":19,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" So consider the message and understand the vision: "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 24:15","book":"Mat","chapter":24,"verse":15,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dn 10:11","book":"Dan","chapter":10,"verse":11},{"label":"Dn 10:19","book":"Dan","chapter":10,"verse":19},{"label":"Mt 24:15","book":"Mat","chapter":24,"verse":15}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"by God added for clarity"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Dan:9:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Seventy weeks are decreed "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 25:8","book":"Lev","chapter":25,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 14:34","book":"Num","chapter":14,"verse":34,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 4:5–6","book":"Ezk","chapter":4,"verse":5,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lv 25:8","book":"Lev","chapter":25,"verse":8},{"label":"Nm 14:34","book":"Num","chapter":14,"verse":34},{"label":"Ezk 4:5–6","book":"Ezk","chapter":4,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Dan:9:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Know and understand this:"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Dan:9:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"After those sixty-two weeks"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Dan:9:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He will make a firm covenant "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or will enforce a covenant"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or will enforce a covenant"}]}]},"cachedAt":1783099473140}